input.command:
sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claude-code-claimdb/test_dbs/california_schools.sqlite" "
SELECT 
  \"Free Meal Count (Ages 5-17)\",
  \"Enrollment (Ages 5-17)\",
  ROUND(\"Free Meal Count (Ages 5-17)\" * 100.0 / \"Enrollment (Ages 5-17)\", 2) AS free_rate
FROM frpm
WHERE \"Educational Option Type\" = 'Continuation School'
  AND \"Enrollment (Ages 5-17)\" > 0
  AND \"Free Meal Count (Ages 5-17)\" IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY free_rate ASC
LIMIT 5;
"
